@ComricFraudCalculatorBackend_HostAddress = https://localhost:7xxx
@token = {{auth_token}}

### Exchange client credentials for JWT (Azure Entra ID)
POST {{ComricFraudCalculatorBackend_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": "YOUR_CLIENT_APP_ID",
  "clientSecret": "YOUR_CLIENT_SECRET",
  "scope": "Events.Read Events.Write Signals.Read Audit.Read Dashboard.Read"
}

### Submit HR fraud event
POST {{ComricFraudCalculatorBackend_HostAddress}}/api/v1/hr-events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idNumber": "8501015800084",
  "eventType": "GhostEmployee",
  "eventDate": "2026-03-15T00:00:00Z",
  "employerName": "Acme Holdings (Pty) Ltd",
  "employeeNumber": "EMP-4521",
  "verificationStatus": "Denied",
  "notes": "Employee does not appear on company payroll."
}

### Submit MNO fraud event
POST {{ComricFraudCalculatorBackend_HostAddress}}/api/v1/mno-events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idNumber": "8501015800084",
  "msisdn": "0821234567",
  "eventType": "NewSIMApplication",
  "eventDate": "2026-03-16T10:30:00Z",
  "applicationChannel": "InStore",
  "outletOrDealer": "CellShop Sandton City",
  "deviceImei": "356938035643809",
  "flagReason": "Third SIM application in 7 days. Velocity threshold exceeded."
}

### Anonymous fraud signals feed
GET {{ComricFraudCalculatorBackend_HostAddress}}/api/v1/fraud-signals?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ID lookup (hashed before query)
POST {{ComricFraudCalculatorBackend_HostAddress}}/api/v1/lookup/id-check
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idNumber": "8501015800084"
}

### Dashboard stats (tenant-scoped)
GET {{ComricFraudCalculatorBackend_HostAddress}}/api/v1/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Activity log (tenant-scoped)
GET {{ComricFraudCalculatorBackend_HostAddress}}/api/v1/activity-log?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
